## How Articles Are Structured

Every deep-dive article follows the same pattern:

- **Level badge** — Beginner / Intermediate / Advanced
- **Pre-reading links** — what to read first
- **Concept explanation** — clear prose + tables
- **Diagram** — visual of how it works
- **Math section** — equations explained step-by-step (where applicable)
- **Interview Q&A** — common questions with model answers
- **Hover glossary** — underlined terms show definitions on hover

